        <h2 class="mb-3">Objectives</h2>
        <p>
            The primary objective of the School Management System is to modernize and automate key tasks such as student enrollment, course management, etc. By centralizing these processes into a single platform, the system aims to improve efficiency, accuracy, and communication within schools.
        </p>
