            <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Organization:</strong> Centralize data and information, making it easier to access, update, and analyze critical school-related data.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Communication:</strong> Improve communication between administrators, teachers, parents, and students through integrated messaging and notification features.</li>
